1. Datasets
-----------

This repository contains no dataset records, no network traffic, no sensor
measurements, and no labels. Nothing here can be used to train or evaluate a
detector.

What it contains is a mapping: for each of ten ICS and IIoT intrusion-detection
datasets, the ATT&CK for ICS techniques that the dataset's own authors
documented, together with the passage of their paper or release documentation
that supports each assignment.

Each dataset remains the property of its authors and is governed by its own
terms of distribution. Some are downloaded from a public page; others require a
request to the authors or the operating institution, and some carry a data-use
agreement. Obtain each dataset from its published source, or by request to its
authors, and comply with the terms they set. This repository confers no right
of access to any of them.

The ten datasets, with the DOI of the paper that introduces each, are listed in
data/dataset_meta.csv.


