3. Quoted passages
------------------

data/mapping_evidence.csv and data/EVIDENCE_LOG.md quote short passages,
verbatim and with attribution, from the papers and release documentation of the
ten datasets. The quotations exist so that every mapped technique can be traced
to the sentence that justifies it, which is what makes the mapping auditable
rather than asserted.

Copyright in those sentences remains with their authors and publishers. The
CC BY 4.0 licence in LICENSE-DATA covers our selection, arrangement, and
analysis. It does not cover the quoted sentences, and it cannot: we do not own
them. Anyone reusing the evidence file should cite the dataset papers, not only
this repository.
